criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient with a documented AAA (CT-scan or ultrasound less than 6 months before
             enrollment) with a maximum diameter (max D) between 4.5 cm and 7 cm.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Ruptured, symptomatic or not atheromatous aneurysm;

          -  Renal failure (renal serum clearance <50 mL/min);

          -  Previous intervention on AAA (general or endovascular surgery);

          -  BMI >35;

          -  Atrial fibrillation.
